title: The history of the grand visiers, Mahomet and Achmet Coprogli, of the three last grand signiors, their Sultana's and chief favourites, with the most secret intrigues of the seraglio besides several other particulars of the wars of Dalmatia, Transylvania, Hungary, Candia, and Poland / Englished by John Evelyn, Junior.
author: Chassepol, François de, 17th cent.
notes: Translation of: Histoire des grands vizirs Mahomet Caprogli-pacha et Achmet Caprogli-pacha.
